reviewText: Amazing show 100 times better than US version. However this price is insane and I feel it's a price gouging at its finest. This is available on amazon UK for 44pounds that's 56$ US
Great Cast, creative stories - every once in a while need to turn on subs cause I just missed what they said. Damn funny.
Love this was hooked the first time I watched.

We enjoy, every time, when we watching , the movies, some we seen twice, in the Netherlands  and USA .
